sources.title: Western Pacific Agent (1950) COLORIZED | Noir Crime Drama | Full Length Movie
sources.description:
STOP . . . KILLER ON A RAMPAGE! LOOK . . . VIOLENCE RIDES THE RAILS! 
A psychotic hobo kills two people while committing a payroll robbery and Western Pacific Agent Rod Kendall is on the case.

Watch the original Black & White version: https://youtu.be/jP53uvdt5LE

Director: Sam Newfield
Writers: Milton Raison, Fred Myton
Stars: Kent Taylor, Sheila Ryan, Mickey Knox & Sid Melton
Genres: Classics, Colorized, Crime Drama, Film-Noir
